  "body": "Edit: the reproduction currently doesn't work, closing temporarily.\r\n\r\nOn MacOS with non case-senstive file system (the default):\r\n```\r\nmkdir Project\r\ncd Project\r\nnpm init --yes\r\nnpm install --save-dev hardhat\r\nhardhat # basic sample project + all defaults\r\ncd ../project # wrong case\r\nhardhat\r\n```\r\nThe last command would fail with\r\n```\r\nError HH12: Trying to use a non-local installation of Hardhat, which is not supported.\r\nPlease install Hardhat locally using npm or Yarn, and try again.\r\n\r\nFor more info go to https://hardhat.org/HH12 or run Hardhat with --show-stack-traces\r\n```\r\n",
